{"tid":1708072,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"加利尼維利表示，哥迪奧拿應當嘗試一下三後衛","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T05:58:02.000Z","uid":173952,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"57051c49efa0c98166ab76ca881aad988a84a3d7","tid":1708072,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:56:44.000Z","msg":"在曼城1-3輸給利物浦後，《天空體育》評論員加利尼維利（Gary Neville）表示，哥迪奧拿（Pep Guardiola）在今場比賽應當嘗試一下三後衛體系，有可能球隊會有更出色的表現。<br />\n<br />\n  尼維利在《天空體育》的節目中這樣談道：「我認為哥迪奧拿在過去的兩三個星期里一直在考慮這場比賽，我只是覺得他這場比賽會向我們展示出一些不同的東西。但我得到的和往常一樣&mdash;&mdash;可能報紙和我們在今天早上已經談論了這些事情。」<br />\n<br />\n  「從足球的角度來看，曼城踢得很好，但他們後衛線上的四名球員和門將一直未能跟上節奏。在這裡比賽你必須要充滿信心，也許三後衛的體系表現會更好一些。」<br />\n<br />\n  「富有創新精神，保持創造力，這就是我對哥迪奧拿的期望，這場比賽不太像他。」"},{"pid":"1964e8cf9340e5fc52e682ecc3e8f6aad0fe16b8","tid":1708072,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"不如曼聯名宿黎教啦"},{"pid":"fc2f45601ff39828f938577aeb70a477373cb577","tid":1708072,"uid":215570,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"搵bravo守龍 三十個後衛都救佢唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320b159a0d276cf56951f9f79dc7f0a45010